entry.title: Migrant Influx Overwhelms Southern Border as Title 42 Winds Down
entry.content: The pandemic-era border measure that has served as a blunt border-enforcement tool for two successive administrations is set to end Thursday night.

entry.title: Zelensky Urges Caution on Timing of Counteroffensive as Ukraine Advances in Bakhmut
entry.content: Ukraine made further gains against Russian forces in the eastern city of Bakhmut, as President Zelensky said the military needs more time before it can launch a much-anticipated major counteroffensive to recapture territory it has lost.
